	<name>PHPIDS</name>
	<channel>pear.php.net</channel>
	<summary>Easy to use Web application security layer</summary>
	<description>
		This package provides an easy to use intrusion detection systems (IDS) which 
		is capable of detecting malicious user input and reaction on configurable ways 
		to protect the security of the application the IDSD is used with.
		
		Most of the provided filter rules detect XSS attacks, directory traversals and 
		several different SQL Injections attempts. The filter rules can easily be extended. 
	</description>
